\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2011/02/broccoli-shells-n-cheese/#comment-56056\">03.26.11 at 3:30 pm</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>Packaged, preshredded cheese is coated with chemicals to prevent clumping and can also make it difficult to melt smoothly&#8211;that may explain the issues with melting posted above.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/02/broccoli-shells-n-cheese/?replytocom=56056#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-56056\", \"56056\", \"respond\", \"13351\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"comment-56148\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41dc3e007986c35dc46763689fa93174?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\">Allison</cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2011/02/broccoli-shells-n-cheese/#comment-56148\">04.09.11 at 12:42 pm</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>I just made this and it was so yummy!! Thanks!!</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/02/broccoli-shells-n-cheese/?replytocom=56148#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-56148\", \"56148\", \"respond\", \"13351\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"comment-56174\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment