-jasmine-rice/\" title=\"yellow jasmine rice\" class=\"alignnone\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Yellow-Rice-side-200x150.jpg\" class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"Yellow Jasmine Rice\" /></a><h2><a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2011/07/yellow-jasmine-rice/\" title=\"yellow jasmine rice\">yellow jasmine rice</a></h2></div><!--end post_class()-->\n\n<div class=\"post-13264 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-breakfast category-dessert category-oats category-vegetables category-vegetarian entry gfwa-8 gfwa-even\"><a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2011/09/baked-pumpkin-pie-oatmeal/\" title=\"baked pumpkin pie oatmeal\" class=\"alignnone\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Baked-Pumpkin-Oatmeal-close-200x150.jpg\" class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"Baked Pumpkin Pie Oatmeal\" /></a><h2><a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2011/09/baked-pumpkin-pie-oatmeal/\" title=\"baked pumpkin pie oatmeal\">baked pumpkin pie oatmeal</a></h2></div><!--end post_class()-->\n\n<div class=\"post-13060 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-beans category-beansandgrains category-global category-main-dish category-southwest category-vegan category-vegetarian entry gfwa-9 gfwa-odd\"><a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2013/04/black-bean-avocado-enchiladas/\" title=\"black bean &amp; avocado enchiladas\" class=\"alignnone\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Black-Bean-Avocado-Enchiladas-front-200x150.jpg\" class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"Black Bean Avocado Enchiladas\" /></a><h2><a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2013/04/black-bean-avocado-enchiladas/\" title=\"black bean &amp; avocado enchiladas\">black bean &amp; avocado enchiladas</a></h2></div><!--end post_class()-->\n\n<div class=\"post-14756 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-beans category-beansandgrains category-br